+++// BCU plays a proc's SE at the moment the effect is actually applied to a target
+++// Entity, not when the attack rolls the proc:
+++//   Entity.damaged: POIATK with rst != 100 -> basis.lea.add(A_POISON) + setSE(SE_POISON)
